{"parentUuid":"9c6601b8-a97e-40c5-816f-62d286b0d55d","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/skogix/.local/share/containers","sessionId":"b9e8251b-c2cb-4ad4-b79e-9eb7c996b007","version":"2.1.62","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"rosy-whistling-horizon","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01RjQ4LrNqJjLcxpSZjtpt5R","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Parses cleanly. The structure:\n\n```\nargc up / down          # all services at once\nargc list               # podman ps -a\nargc container <args>   # raw podman container passthrough\n\nargc searxng up         # start searxng\nargc searxng down       # stop\nargc searxng logs [-f]  # logs, optional follow\nargc searxng shell      # root shell in container\n```\n\n`searxng up` is idempotent — if the container already exists it does `podman start` instead of re-creating it. Want to add more services or wire this into systemd/a quadlet?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":193,"cache_read_input_tokens":50020,"output_tokens":147,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":193,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYafbZFoYkCDVywawrmUZ","type":"assistant","uuid":"f0d8b603-81af-4401-bfd1-b1a55363f47d","timestamp":"2026-02-28T15:00:00.637Z"}
